{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM08_080.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x16,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hey, Plachta? Can I ask you something?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "What is it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Why did you and Luard start wanting to use alchemy to make people happy?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I was thinking that if we know that, it might be easier to persuade him."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "A reason? ...It really wasn't much."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I don't mind. Will you tell me?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "...I believe it was when we were still around your age, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "One year, the village we were living in experienced a drought, and our crops grew poorly."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Luard and I wanted to do something about it, so we gathered books from around the village, and learned about alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "We studied alchemy, thought of new recipes, and created an item... And we managed to solve the village's problem."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x6a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I still recall how grateful the people of the village were to us, and it was a joyous occasion."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x6a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Thinking back now, I believe that was the reason why Luard and I started pursuing the same dream."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I see... So something like that happened..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Hey, I was just thinking, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Maybe we could make the item you created way back then?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x6b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "The item...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "It was the item that started your dream, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Maybe if he saw that, Luard would remember what his real dream was, too!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "...I understand. It should be worth trying, if you believe that strongly about it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x44,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "I'll give you the recipe. It was something we could make way back then, so it should be simple for you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Thank you, Plachta! I'll make it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Received \"<CLGR>Recipe of Origin<CLNR>\", \"<CLGR>Moisture Grass<CLNR>\"."
        }
    ]
}